  "name": "Blistering Feint",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/fire_13.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your foes flinch from the heat of your weapon, giving you an opportunity to slip past their defenses.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Combat Expertise, Improved Feint, ifrit.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You gain a +2 bonus on feint checks made while wielding a weapon that deals fire damage. Anytime you successfully feint a creature while using such a weapon, you may deal its fire damage to the enemy.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you attempt a feint while you're wielding a weapon that deals fire damage, you can spend up to 5 stamina points to gain a bonus on the Bluff check equal to the number of stamina points you spent.",
